   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-accepting-acceptted" mid="72" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>But even if it really is Tryan's command scroll, we can't open it right away. I'll ask the sorceresses under me to find a way to break the spell that seals the scroll. Your identity has been revealed to the Army of Destruction now so you should stay low for the time being.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-" mid="42" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Great. I was worried about the strange man in Hiver's barn... I should go and take a look.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-a" mid="43" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Oh! <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-b" mid="44" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>You knocked off early, Grele?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-c" mid="45" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Yup, Hiver is busy on an important mission and my big brother's away too so I thought I should look after my siblings. I'm trying to come back home to see them whenever I have the time.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-d" mid="46" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>But the guy in the barn isn't doing anything bad... Could I have mistaken him…?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-e" mid="47" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>It's better to be safe than sorry.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-f" mid="48" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>You must be here after promising me you'd come, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. I heard from my sister that…<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Grele suddenly lowers his voice)</FONT><BR>You're from <FONT color=#a82424>Lagendia</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-g" mid="49" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Don't be alarmed! I'm very proud of my sister and I want to follow her footsteps one day... I mean, what I'm saying is, I know what she's doing!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-h" mid="50" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>…No worries, Grele. I know you'll keep my secret.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-i" mid="51" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>…I heard that the good side of us is originally from Lagendia... And seeing someone from Lagendia with my own eyes, you're much nicer than I expected... You remind me of my big brother…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-j" mid="52" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>He is very loving and he played with me a lot. He said... Hiver and I should take care of the family when he's away... I miss him… I heard the labour at Goldstone Mine is notoriously hard. I hope I can hear any news about him and know that he's doing well...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-k" mid="53" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>……Is there any way you can find some news about your brother?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-l" mid="54" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Don't worry, I'll help you.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-l" mid="55" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You're young enough to throw tantrums. Don't worry.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-l" mid="56" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>It's not hard to go to Merca from here.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Erm…… Maybe the <FONT color=#a82424>Goldstone Merchant</FONT> at Merca's Heart might know about the mine labourers. But I'm busy with the carpet factory... and my sister seems to be in contact with my brother but all she tells me is that he's doing well. I don't want to throw tantrum and ask her to tell me more about his news…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-m" mid="57" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Really? Would you really go and find my brother's news for me, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Grele brightens up.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-1-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-2" mid="58" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Vernicka told me to stay low but... I guess I just have to stay away from Tryan and his gang.)<BR>Yeah, leave it to me.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-" mid="59" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(There's a merchant who looks just like Lagendia's Merchant Pania.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1820_cradle_grele-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1820_cradle_grele-2-" mid="60" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>My brother's name is <FONT color=#a82424>Guy</FONT>. The goldstone merchant is a <FONT color=#a82424>hybrid with a bird that carries a lot of stuff</FONT> so you'll be able to find her easily. I'll go back to the Blue Wind Plains so please come and find me there when you find any news.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-a" mid="62" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(A hybrid with a loaded bird… I could guess who that might be like but this merchant really looks like </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Pania</FONT><FONT color=#662500>! Could it be another duplicate from Lagendia…?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-b" mid="63" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Do you need anything? By the way, if you're here to look for <FONT color=#a82424>Merchant Fargeau</FONT>, it's me, the furry cat hybrid not my bird friend!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-c" mid="64" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I know you're Merchant Fargeau. I was wondering if you know about the labourers in the Goldstone Mine since you trade goldstones.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-d" mid="65" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Fargeau tidies his whiskers.)</FONT><BR>Yup! I'm Merchant Fargeau who trades goldstones! But...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-e" mid="66" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Wait a minute, you're the one who's been helping out Vernicka recently!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-f" mid="67" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Oh, you don't need to be on guard.<BR>The merchants in Merca's Heart work closely with the <FONT color=#a82424>City Headquarters</FONT> so I know about you. It's not like I've been spying on you or whatever.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-g" mid="68" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>I want to help you for Vernicka's sake, but… There are many Goldstone Mines and hundreds of labourers are working there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-h" mid="69" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Besides, the labourers often collapse from the hard labour and they get replaced on a regular basis. I don't know who you're looking for but I need to do my research first.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-i" mid="73" select_type="4" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-!next" mid="71" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Fargeau suddenly twitches his nose like he has thought of something.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
